          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Foreclosure Fairness Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a court, in the case of any federally related mortgage loan, from entering a deficiency judgment requiring the mortgagor to pay any remaining balance on the mortgage loan after a foreclosure sale of the mortgaged property.</p>]]></text>
